Job Details
Looking for three bright females and two males to fill roles in both Abu Dhabi and Dubai. Two shops will be opening soon and require a total of five Ice Cream stewards.
Individuals must have good customer service and must be a quick learner. Food and beverage experience would add value but not essential however customer service experience is a necessity.
Requirements
Fluent in English
Customer Service Experience
Quick learner
